{"tid":2167512,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳彥霖死因研訊下周一開庭 預計審期11天","createTime":"2020-08-21T07:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T16:32:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf0bfe36eae75df91c99c9a0bf54bff9e3430f1","tid":2167512,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:05:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/KHSRDL7LWZDBRBXDDKDCICFSIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FKHSRDL7LWZDBRBXDDKDCICFSIU%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=8e3f47d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FKHSRDL7LWZDBRBXDDKDCICFSIU%2F&h=418d5f39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/KHSRDL7LWZDBRBXDDKDCICFSIU/</a><br />\n<br />\n曾參與反送中集會的15歲職訓局青年書院女生陳彥霖，去年9月底離奇赤裸浮屍海面，警方及後指死因無可疑。死因裁判法庭決定就案件召開研訊，並會傳召十多名證人。研訊將於下周一早上9時半開審，預計審訊11天。"},{"pid":"a20f0db625a3e55134cc1d17db9f0f033f309b99","tid":2167512,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b2973498790cb7e6297a88572b018800ac7167","tid":2167512,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1862c432e12594b37e3d34504abf63c3f31fa97","tid":2167512,"uid":35081,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:06:41.000Z","msg":"希望搵到真